descriptions: You can download a trial version of this app to try it for 15 minutes for free.
You won’t be charged anything when this free trial ends. You can’t make in-app purchases or use add-on content during this free trial, but you’ll keep any achievements you earn.

display_long_description:
**COOK AND SERVE**

Your main task is to prepare the correct recipe and deliver it. Customers will line up, and you must deliver their order in time. Prepare the ingredients before the start of the day.
[media]
**SLICE THEM UP**

Slice your food anyway you want but don't burn the fries!
[media]
**CRAZY BURGERS**

Gourmet customers will have extraordinary orders.
[media]
**YOUR SETUP**

Customize your layout. Your truck, your rules!
[media]
**PLAY NOW**

Buy new trucks, new equipment and discover the real challenge. 
[media]
